</span> Incense, frankincense</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">References:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">לְבוֹנָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(lvonah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:34\">EXO 30:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:1\">LEV 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:2\">LEV 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:15\">LEV 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:16\">LEV 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11\">LEV 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:8\">LEV 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:7\">LEV 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:15\">NUM 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:29\">1CH 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:5\">NEH 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:9\">NEH 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:6\">SNG 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:6\">SNG 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:14\">SNG 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:23\">ISA 43:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:6\">ISA 60:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:3\">ISA 66:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:20\">JER 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:26\">JER 17:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:5\">JER 41:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">נִיחוֹחַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(nichoach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:10\">EZR 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:46\">DAN 2:46</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">קטר, קִטֵּר, קְטוֹרָה, קְטֹרֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(qatar (verb), qiter, qtorah, qtoreth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:6\">EXO 25: